---
import DocsLayout from '../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="Community" description="Feedback, contribution, and community links for Cepress Generator">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Community & Contribution</h1>

  <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
    Cepress Generator is an open-source project. We welcome feedback, suggestions, and contributions from the community.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">📬 Feedback</h2>
  <p class="mb-4">Found a bug? Have an idea for improvement? Feel free to open an issue on GitHub.</p>
  <p class="mb-8">
    👉 <a href="https://github.com/Dziqha/CepressDocs/issues" target="_blank" class="text-primary-600">Submit Feedback</a>
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">🤝 Contribute</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
    <li>Fork the repository</li>
    <li>Make your changes in a new branch</li>
    <li>Submit a pull request with clear description</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">💬 Join the Discussion</h2>
  <p class="mb-4">Have questions or want to connect with others using Cepress?</p>
  <ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
    <li><a href="https://discord.gg/your-invite" target="_blank" class="text-primary-600">Join our Discord</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://github.com/Dziqha/CepressDocs" target="_blank" class="text-primary-600">Visit GitHub Repo</a></li>
  </ul>
</DocsLayout>
